{
  "stem": "23278.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was-- I became very attached to him, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were very, very good friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the time we had a movement in France-- Catholic-- called the [FRENCH], the cross of fire, fire crosses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was something like you could transpose, but very far, the Buchanan type of sort, except not so stupid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were the upper class-- very, very Catholic, very nationalistic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they started to-- to explain that all those German people who came-- first, they were Jews and they were unwanted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the other thing, they were mixed with the fifth column.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came for spying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you have to be careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And to consult with them, it was to be anti-French.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was to be a traitor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So you-- you had to be careful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I have to say that the German refugees-- in particular, the wife of Walter, who had been what you call in America a Jewish princess, who had been spoiled, who was kept precious, frivolous, covered with jewelry, met with her-- met with her friends in the cafes of France.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know how the cafes are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's not like a bar here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's outside and you-- you meet your friends and you talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- they took over particularly the cafes of Dijon, and the French people felt, what are those people doing there?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they kind of-- the people didn't like them very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were too showy, too noisy, too much there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many were there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many of these Jews came?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were quite a few, because they all came to Dijon-- I should have explained it before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the first who-- who migrated from Germany, they stopped in Alsace.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in Alsace, German was spoken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was close in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
